text: Ángel Janiquet (born 25 October 1962) is a Spanish ski jumper. He competed in the normal hill event at the 1984 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1962 births Category:Living people Category:Spanish male ski jumpers Category:Olympic ski jumpers of Spain Category:Ski jumpers at the 1984 Winter Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Barcelona
